{"parentUuid":"15a724fe-bd5c-458c-bbcd-5257af5fca0e","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"96f7ce82-27af-4c04-ae02-270c4873a922","agentId":"ac7c99e6fe1d41e66","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KT2B3sMoFRHUXqpuBAUdQU","type":"tool_result","content":"# AlphaEvolve's Gemini Model Ensemble and Evolutionary Approach\n\n**Ensemble of Models:**\n\"AlphaEvolve leverages an ensemble of state-of-the-art large language models: our fastest and most efficient model, Gemini Flash, maximizes the breadth of ideas explored, while our most powerful model, Gemini Pro, provides critical depth with insightful suggestions.\"\n\n**Evolutionary Framework:**\n\"uses an evolutionary framework to improve upon the most promising ideas\"\n\n**How Models Function as Engine:**\n\"Together, these models propose computer programs that implement algorithmic solutions as code. AlphaEvolve verifies, runs and scores the proposed programs using automated evaluation metrics.\"\n\nThe system works by having the faster Flash model explore broadly while the more capable Pro model contributes deeper insights, then an evolutionary algorithm selects the best-performing generated solutions for continued iteration."}]},"uuid":"31713dc5-b95e-44b8-9256-e1899826ced6","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:36:25.549Z","toolUseResult":{"bytes":151623,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# AlphaEvolve's Gemini Model Ensemble and Evolutionary Approach\n\n**Ensemble of Models:**\n\"AlphaEvolve leverages an ensemble of state-of-the-art large language models: our fastest and most efficient model, Gemini Flash, maximizes the breadth of ideas explored, while our most powerful model, Gemini Pro, provides critical depth with insightful suggestions.\"\n\n**Evolutionary Framework:**\n\"uses an evolutionary framework to improve upon the most promising ideas\"\n\n**How Models Function as Engine:**\n\"Together, these models propose computer programs that implement algorithmic solutions as code. AlphaEvolve verifies, runs and scores the proposed programs using automated evaluation metrics.\"\n\nThe system works by having the faster Flash model explore broadly while the more capable Pro model contributes deeper insights, then an evolutionary algorithm selects the best-performing generated solutions for continued iteration.","durationMs":3592,"url":"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/"},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"15a724fe-bd5c-458c-bbcd-5257af5fca0e","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
{"parentUuid":"6cd8f8f4-5afc-4c42-a10e-67dc9a44164a","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"96f7ce82-27af-4c04-ae02-270c4873a922","agentId":"ac7c99e6fe1d41e66","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RvwUNGSzrMDyMeFmTGeBRE","type":"tool_result","content":"# Exact Quotes from STOP Paper\n\n**Quote 1 - LM not modified:**\n\"Since the language models themselves are not altered, this is not full recursive self-improvement.\"\n\n**Quote 2 - Scaffolding improvement focus:**\n\"We then run this seed improver to improve itself...the resulting improved improver generates programs with significantly better performance than its seed improver.\"\n\nThese statements confirm the paper's central claim: the scaffolding program (the improver itself) is recursively enhanced through self-iteration, while GPT-4 remains unchanged, thus distinguishing this approach from true recursive self-improvement of the underlying model."}]},"uuid":"e681190d-2a76-4f43-93f3-e3b9e13e155d","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:36:25.957Z","toolUseResult":{"bytes":47180,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Exact Quotes from STOP Paper\n\n**Quote 1 - LM not modified:**\n\"Since the language models themselves are not altered, this is not full recursive self-improvement.\"\n\n**Quote 2 - Scaffolding improvement focus:**\n\"We then run this seed improver to improve itself...the resulting improved improver generates programs with significantly better performance than its seed improver.\"\n\nThese statements confirm the paper's central claim: the scaffolding program (the improver itself) is recursively enhanced through self-iteration, while GPT-4 remains unchanged, thus distinguishing this approach from true recursive self-improvement of the underlying model.","durationMs":2718,"url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2310.02304"},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"6cd8f8f4-5afc-4c42-a10e-67dc9a44164a","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72